text: Károly Kulin-Nagy (16 April 1910 - February 1992) was a Hungarian sports shooter. He competed in the trap event at the 1960 Summer Olympics. ==References== Category:1910 births Category:1992 deaths Category:People from Mosonmagyaróvár Category:Hungarian male sport shooters Category:Olympic shooters of Hungary Category:Shooters at the 1960 Summer Olympics
